XVYXVk</a><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">想補做/一次過做任務嘅戰士，睇呢到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<blockquote>終極洗版任務 - <span style=\"color: red;\">夜晚時段由teammate黃心穎(回魂)</span> 發放<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/75759\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/75759</a><br />\n <br />\n50大廣告商任務時間表<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ryhivM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ryhivM&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=1ded8c71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ryhivM</a></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">歡迎用呢幾幅圖去FB留言</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1u619D6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1u619D6.png&h=ffeb70a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/s960x960/74224155_490378655152322_791355193236127744_o.jpg?_nc_cat=104&amp;_nc_ohc=tXIxhMQsJ8UAQn4XB5G7r8mn8u5uB-ULY4irvoTHfKXU_0-_Ok2g4lnMw&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg3-1.fna&amp;oh=df2d1655aeb87c638b079af9398bccec&amp;oe=5E49C4DA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg3-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fs960x960%2F74224155_490378655152322_791355193236127744_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D104%26_nc_ohc%3DtXIxhMQsJ8UAQn4XB5G7r8mn8u5uB-ULY4irvoTHfKXU_0-_Ok2g4lnMw%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg3-1.fna%26oh%3Ddf2d1655aeb87c638b079af9398bccec%26oe%3D5E49C4DA&h=8738b34c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4OFB5XW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4OFB5XW.jpg&h=34f0d91a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得bookmark</span