\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/312Vkgo</a>)<br />\n<br />\n喺同廣告界人士談話之間，發現呢個抵制廣告商運動係堅係好成功~!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多廣告商都唔再落下年廣告</span></span>，團隊成員喺到好想多謝大家一直以嚟嘅努力... 無你哋就唔可能咁成功<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> (當然其實戰士人數未係好夠，需要再多啲戰士幫手)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同時CCTVB驚到震晒，不停想打壓我地.... 喺到我哋想再重伸三大訴求:<br />\n一、解僱袁志偉<br />\n二、承認以往新聞偏頗<br />\n三、設立有效機制以確保新聞客觀持平<br />\n否則我哋將與港人攜手牽起更進一步的抵制行動<br />\n<br />\n廢UP完，親愛的戰士們請做任~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/RsCoj0j.jpg\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:49:40.000Z","msg":"依家先留意到2樓仲有野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n參戰左一排，一直個心態都係想cctvb永遠消失，連改過機會都唔想再比佢，佢翻到身既話香港人一定無運行。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"653510282a25c5e02fe62747444f1264460ef509","tid":1767031,"uid":199882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:58:20.000Z","msg":"攪掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />推到cctvb冚家鏟"},{"pid":"fc567da979a1501c3985aa06267d13225aefce6b","tid":1767031,"uid":156767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T06:58:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fff644b5cb41e24cebea5d78accddb6469b7e6e","tid":1767031,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:05:22.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dd7008be8faa4a976d842fdaa17d947b21af19ce","tid":1767031,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:11:17.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"312bd44599c07d8225abe660fb3a48b9ae9c2756","tid":1767031,"uid":267969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5dc5fac9735d56a124959bd620acd8b9957fe59","tid":1767031,"uid":78392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T05:18:30.000Z","msg":"點解你咁耐仲係p牌<img src=\"/assets/