<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2f804de516d959b5080a1baa902c62011b8fa4","tid":1767031,"uid":143124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T04:31:46.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"85545960cb56705d9c757e52ce913068700db62c","tid":1767031,"uid":267969,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T04:26:24.000Z","msg":"話說我哋同義工們尋日都去左廣告界集會，派左約2千張傳單 (傳單Url: <a href=\"http://bit.ly/312Vkgo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F312Vkgo&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KsWlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=7cae12f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/312Vkgo</a>)<br />\n<br />\n喺同廣告界人士談話之間，發現呢個抵制廣告商運動係堅係好成功~!<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好多廣告商都唔再落下年廣告</span></span>，團隊成員喺到好想多謝大家一直以嚟嘅努力... 無你哋就唔可能咁成功<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> (當然其實戰士人數未係好夠，需要再多啲戰士幫手)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n同時CCTVB驚到震晒，不停想打壓我地.... 喺到我哋想再重伸三大訴求:<br />\n一、解僱袁志偉<br />\n二、承認以往新聞偏頗<br />\n三、設立有效機制以確保新聞客觀持平<br />\n否則我哋將與港人攜手牽起更進一步的抵制行動<br />\n<br />\n廢UP完，親愛的戰士們請做任~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/RsCoj0j.jpg\" />"}}